          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_4eeb2d8a-aaae-4327-a64d-c9f95bbd72f7.jpg",
            "text": "<p>This is the most popular diamond engagement ring shape for a reason. Its symmetry and sparkle symbolize enduring love and perfection. Whether paired with platinum, yellow gold, white gold or rose gold, it adapts effortlessly to every era and outfit.</p>",
