          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Geometric, sharp, and endlessly radiant, this princess cut is the modern bride’s statement. It’s edges sparkle with precision, giving it a sleek, architectural appeal. It’s perfect for those who love clarity and confidence in design </p>",
